<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - ShopMate</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            animation: fadeInPage 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }


        header {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        header nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        header nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        header nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #ff6f61;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 70vh;
            background: url('https://cdn.vectorstock.com/i/500p/39/11/programming-and-software-development-web-page-vector-30433911.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            position: relative;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideIn 2s ease;
        }

      

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            animation: floatIn 1.5s ease-out;
        }

       

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: floatIn 2s ease-out;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
        }

        .about h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: bounceIn 1.5s ease;
        }

       

        .about h2::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 50%;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            margin: 10px auto 0;
            animation: growLine 1s ease;
        }

       

        .about p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
        }

        /* Team Section */
        .team {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
        }

        .team h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounceIn 1.5s ease;
        }

        .team-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .team-card {
            background-color: white;
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            animation: zoomIn 1s ease;
        }

        
       

        .team-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .team-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .team-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 15px 0 5px;
        }

        .team-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Footer Section */
        footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        footer .footer-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        footer .footer-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>About ShopMate</h1>
            <p>Your trusted e-commerce platform with a passion for excellence.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about">
        <h2>OUR STORY</h2>
        <p>ShopMate was founded with a vision to create a seamless online shopping experience. Our goal is to bring the best products from across the globe to your doorstep. With a dedicated team and innovative technology, we are committed to providing exceptional customer service and unmatched quality.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="team">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <div class="team-container">
            <div class="team-card">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/005/346/410/small_2x/close-up-portrait-of-smiling-handsome-young-caucasian-man-face-looking-at-camera-on-isolated-light-gray-studio-background-photo.jpg" alt="Team Member 1">
                <h3>John Doe</h3>
                <p>CEO & Founder</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/005/346/410/small_2x/close-up-portrait-of-smiling-handsome-young-caucasian-man-face-looking-at-camera-on-isolated-light-gray-studio-background-photo.jpg" alt="Team Member 2">
                <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                <p>Head of Marketing</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/005/346/410/small_2x/close-up-portrait-of-smiling-handsome-young-caucasian-man-face-looking-at-camera-on-isolated-light-gray-studio-background-photo.jpg" alt="Team Member 3">
                <h3>Mark Wilson</h3>
                <p>Lead Developer</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
